  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 150 unique monsters! A massive RPG with an abundance of rich content.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Train your monster with the goal of becoming the champion!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only the main character's partner possesses the cheat move called \"Cheat Tackle\".</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It ensures a guaranteed first strike and a one-hit kill.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the easy mode, you can even use it endlessly!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696050/extras/f1046b481ae9e1016e00167b558e8a3f.poster.avif?t=1774056947\" width=598 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696050/extras/f1046b481ae9e1016e00167b558e8a3f.webm?t=1774056947\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696050/extras/f1046b481ae9e1016e00167b558e8a3f.mp4?t=1774056947\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696050/extras/e23efea781bc07883110418ef3aae552.webp?t=1774056947\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this world, there exists mystical creatures known as \"Yarimon\".</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Known as the loner protagonist with the weakest Yarimon... until now, that is. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a surprising turn of events, the protagonist's Yarimon partner learned a godly-powerful move with a power level of 800,000 called the \"Cheat Tackle\". </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With this, the protagonist's world completely changed, as this move will one-shot any opponent in battle (though it is only usable once per battle). </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Of course, it would be foolish to believe that one can become the champion with just a single move. Therefore, a trainer must continue to hone their skills and diversify their strategies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With that said, defeating my childhood friend for the first time is already a crazy accomplishment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I can finally get back some of the money I lost to her...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Afterwards, I set out on an adventure after my childhood friend told me she was going on a journey and pressured me to do the same. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696050/extras/9a0c13dc5f0ce5186f6f2ebc78edc77f.poster.avif?t=1774056947\" width=596 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696050/extras/9a0c13dc5f0ce5186f6f2ebc78edc77f.webm?t=1774056947\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696050/extras/9a0c13dc5f0ce5186f6f2ebc78edc77f.mp4?t=1774056947\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As I am adventuring, I slowly unravel the secret of this world. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is when I felt like my journey had really begun.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Aim to complete the Yarimon Encyclopedia (Yaridex)!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696050/extras/b6c4d961794151a164796165ab45acc4.poster.avif?t=1774056947\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696050/extras/b6c4d961794151a164796165ab45acc4.webm?t=1774056947\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696050/extras/b6c4d961794151a164796165ab45acc4.mp4?t=1774056947\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696050/extras/0571469e14ccf4be1c12270501251fe7.webp?t=1774056947\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Monster-taming RPG</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect a variety of Yarimon and strive relentlessly towards the championship!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gain EXP by battling either wild Yarimon or trainers. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With the advent of EXP shards, you will also be able to freely allocate EXP to your favorite Yarimon!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover the truth and secrets that are hidden within this world!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the secrets hidden in this world, gradually unveiling it's truth!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 150 monsters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pixel art for each character</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Illustrations for each character along with various facial expressions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Having a monster index</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 150 unique monsters! A massive RPG with an abundance of rich content.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Train your monster with the goal of becoming the champion!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only the main character's partner possesses the cheat move called \"Cheat Tackle\".</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It ensures a guaranteed first strike and a one-hit kill.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the easy mode, you can even use it endlessly!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696050/extras/f1046b481ae9e1016e00167b558e8a3f.poster.avif?t=1774056947\" width=598 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696050/extras/f1046b481ae9e1016e00167b558e8a3f.webm?t=1774056947\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696050/extras/f1046b481ae9e1016e00167b558e8a3f.mp4?t=1774056947\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696050/extras/e23efea781bc07883110418ef3aae552.webp?t=1774056947\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this world, there exists mystical creatures known as \"Yarimon\".</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Known as the loner protagonist with the weakest Yarimon... until now, that is. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a surprising turn of events, the protagonist's Yarimon partner learned a godly-powerful move with a power level of 800,000 called the \"Cheat Tackle\". </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With this, the protagonist's world completely changed, as this move will one-shot any opponent in battle (though it is only usable once per battle). </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Of course, it would be foolish to believe that one can become the champion with just a single move. Therefore, a trainer must continue to hone their skills and diversify their strategies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With that said, defeating my childhood friend for the first time is already a crazy accomplishment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I can finally get back some of the money I lost to her...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Afterwards, I set out on an adventure after my childhood friend told me she was going on a journey and pressured me to do the same. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696050/extras/9a0c13dc5f0ce5186f6f2ebc78edc77f.poster.avif?t=1774056947\" width=596 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696050/extras/9a0c13dc5f0ce5186f6f2ebc78edc77f.webm?t=1774056947\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696050/extras/9a0c13dc5f0ce5186f6f2ebc78edc77f.mp4?t=1774056947\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As I am adventuring, I slowly unravel the secret of this world. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is when I felt like my journey had really begun.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Aim to complete the Yarimon Encyclopedia (Yaridex)!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696050/extras/b6c4d961794151a164796165ab45acc4.poster.avif?t=1774056947\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696050/extras/b6c4d961794151a164796165ab45acc4.webm?t=1774056947\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696050/extras/b6c4d961794151a164796165ab45acc4.mp4?t=1774056947\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696050/extras/0571469e14ccf4be1c12270501251fe7.webp?t=1774056947\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Monster-taming RPG</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect a variety of Yarimon and strive relentlessly towards the championship!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gain EXP by battling either wild Yarimon or trainers. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With the advent of EXP shards, you will also be able to freely allocate EXP to your favorite Yarimon!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover the truth and secrets that are hidden within this world!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the secrets hidden in this world, gradually unveiling it's truth!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 150 monsters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pixel art for each character</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Illustrations for each character along with various facial expressions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Having a monster index</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
